name: #33. Carl The Stargazer
description:
A dreamer. A lover. Certainly not a fighter. We are all tiny specks of dust. But this tiny speck shines brighter than most. 


“What’s a bunny’s favourite music?”
“What do you call a rabbit comedian?”
“What is orange and sounds like a parrot?”
“How can you say rabbit without using the letter R?”


'r' toggles auto-rotate. ‘l’ toggles mouse following

Artist: radarboy3000 (https://twitter.com/radarboy3000)
